ockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>狗公都有人吹奏，食撚屎啦屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n唔抵得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>有咩唔抵得？？唔抵得你個閪咁臭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肉酸到，唔夠人講就話人閪臭，同某啲連登仔講全部女人都係雞一樣咁核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>中意埋D狗公，仲煩到日日吹奏，唔係臭閪係乜野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我鍾意睇藝人就叫臭閪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你憑嗰啲咁耐以嚟得文字無相嘅新聞去話佢狗公咪蠢撚都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b252ff70a85c21f179fa4102b9a0e66844fa5a","tid":525221,"uid":56716,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"唔怪得叫香港豬啦，原來真係無腦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0bc78c9ff2e471b8d021404e1a2ae800f82ff9","tid":525221,"uid":27210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"又炒作"},{"pid":"989ad0a0fca59e30bcd0369fc04be80d43486d7a","tid":525221,"uid":56716,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又炒作</blockquote><br />\n就嚟頒獎禮，唔知是咪有人想攞視后借啲意搵搵野搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdefbff8eb55b47c3b81d5ce042b3373d3a3279","tid":525221,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"58b252ff70a85c21f179fa4102b9a0e66844fa5a","tid":525221,"uid":56716,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"唔怪得叫香港豬啦，原來真係無腦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20